- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is also a possible category as public announcement logic is often used in the study of multiagent systems. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with the completeness of public announcement logic in different models, which involves the study of algorithms and data structures.
